1
00:00:00,810 --> 00:00:03,740
You also killed Bok Gil.
But that's not all, is it?

2
00:00:03,980 --> 00:00:06,910
You killed my daughter, Seo Rin,
with your own two hands.

3
00:00:07,510 --> 00:00:09,180
Did you think I'd let you
get away with it?

4
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:13,350
Jung Suk Hee, you've come to your senses?

5
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:16,250
So it was all an act this whole time?

6
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:18,960
Get ready to pay for all of your crimes.

7
00:00:20,690 --> 00:00:21,930
Ali...

8
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:23,630
Jung Suk Hee, you're Ali, aren't you?

9
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:25,300
My 30 million dollars...

10
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:29,230
You're the one who stole
my 30 million dollars, aren't you?

11
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,270
- Let go.
- Chae Hwa Young, you wench!

12
00:00:33,270 --> 00:00:35,470
You still don't understand
what's going on, do you?

13
00:00:36,210 --> 00:00:38,980
Even now, you're still looking
for that 30 million dollars?

14
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:43,380
Is money all you care about?

15
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:46,250
You always put money
before people, don't you?

16
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:49,320
You half-wit. Who do you think
you are, lecturing me?

17
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:54,530
A half-wit?
Do you have any idea who's responsible...

18
00:00:54,590 --> 00:00:57,230
for the 30 years I spent
being scorned by everyone?

19
00:00:57,730 --> 00:01:00,800
As if that wasn't enough,
you took Bok Gil's life...

20
00:01:00,970 --> 00:01:03,800
and exploited Seo Rin,
the daughter I gave birth to,

21
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:05,500
and ultimately caused her death?

22
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:08,940
Let go. You keep calling me a murderer.

23
00:01:09,070 --> 00:01:10,940
Who are you saying I killed?

24
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,980
Do you have any proof?

25
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:18,020
Proof? Your own words are the proof.

26
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:23,120
Until you confess
all the horrible things you've done,

27
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:26,060
- you're not taking one step out of here.
- Secretary Kim.

28
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:27,730
Take her phone.

29
00:01:28,030 --> 00:01:30,460
And lock that door tight.

30
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:34,870
No, Dad. You can't do this, please!

31
00:01:35,670 --> 00:01:36,970
Dad...

32
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:40,410
No, Chairman, please spare me.

33
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:45,110
Do you still think I'm your father?

34
00:01:45,210 --> 00:01:49,880
Are you still delusional enough to think
you're the head of Dream Hotel?

35
00:01:49,980 --> 00:01:53,750
You're misunderstanding.
Please, just think about it.

36
00:01:54,090 --> 00:01:58,260
For the past 30 years, I was the one
who took care of Dream and served you.

37
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,320
Shut up!

38
00:01:59,890 --> 00:02:03,390
You were blinded by money and greed.

39
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:05,500
That's the only reason
you stayed by my side.

40
00:02:07,770 --> 00:02:08,770
Father.

41
00:02:09,970 --> 00:02:11,640
If you do this to me,

42
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,140
you will regret it.

43
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:17,310
Surely you know I have
many supporters at the company.

44
00:02:17,510 --> 00:02:18,640
What?

45
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:21,850
I can't believe this wench!

46
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:26,680
Do you not understand
the situation you're in?

47
00:02:29,490 --> 00:02:30,660
Tell me now.

48
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:33,090
Tell me how you killed my Seo Rin.

49
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:36,430
Tell me now!

50
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:38,430
I raised Seo Rin. Why would I kill her?

51
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:41,200
It's no use trying to hold out
by hiding the truth.

52
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,600
Chae Hwa Young.

53
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:44,840
I'll make you pay
for killing my father too.

54
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:47,010
- You demon.
- Let go of me!

55
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:50,340
Listen to me and listen carefully.

56
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:54,380
You will stay here,
and no one will ever know.

57
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:59,620
You'll slowly wither and die,
paying for your sins.

58
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:03,050
This is my punishment for you.

59
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:07,960
- Chairman...
- All of my wealth and company shares...

60
00:03:08,260 --> 00:03:13,060
will be passed on to my daughter, Suk Hee,
and my granddaughter, Jang Mi.

61
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:16,730
You won't get your hands
on a single penny.

62
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:20,670
You're going to wither away
and die in here.

63
00:03:21,370 --> 00:03:23,310
No way...

64
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:26,240
Chae Hwa Young, you will repent in here.

65
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,280
Secretary Kim.

66
00:03:27,850 --> 00:03:31,650
Let her wither away and die in here
like a rat.

67
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:35,320
Don't give her a single drop of water
or a grain of rice.

68
00:03:35,890 --> 00:03:39,390
Under no circumstances
are you to open this door.

69
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:40,790
You witch...

70
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:42,090
Yes, Chairman.

71
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:46,060
No...

72
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,540
Chae Hwa Young.
If you really want to get out of here,

73
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:53,040
you'll have to truly repent for your sins.

74
00:03:54,970 --> 00:03:57,440
No, let go. Let go of me.

75
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,740
I said, let go!

76
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:04,880
No!

77
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:08,750
Open the door. I said, open the door!

78
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:12,260
Hey, you cunning old fox.

79
00:04:12,690 --> 00:04:14,330
Open the door right now.

80
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:16,430
Open the door!

81
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:22,070
Kang Hyuk.

82
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,300
Kang Hyuk.

83
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:27,740
What am I going to do?

84
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:32,210
Open the door.

85
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:41,020
Inform everyone at the company...

86
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:45,490
that she's on an overseas business trip
to improve our hotel's competitiveness...

87
00:04:45,490 --> 00:04:46,560
and to secure foreign investment.

88
00:04:47,490 --> 00:04:50,260
Just say briefly that
it's a highly sensitive lobbying job...

89
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:54,330
that we're only using unofficial channels.

90
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,800
Yes, I understand.

91
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,500
Also tell them
Chae Hwa Young left her phone behind.

92
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:03,270
I'm her only point of contact,
and she's unreachable otherwise.

93
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:05,340
- Got it?
- Yes.

94
00:05:09,610 --> 00:05:11,250
CEO Chae isn't in her room.

95
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:14,050
She must have gone in to work early today.

96
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:17,890
I sent her on a business trip to the US
early this morning.

97
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,660
I see.

98
00:05:20,290 --> 00:05:23,800
Suk Hee, could you reheat Hong Ju's soup?

99
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,200
I'm sure it's cold by now.

100
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:28,130
Who are you to order her to reheat soup?

101
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,370
Is Jang Mi's mom our housekeeper?

102
00:05:30,970 --> 00:05:32,900
What gives you the right
to order her around like that?

103
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,170
Goodness.

104
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:36,010
Honey.

105
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,680
This isn't the first time
I've asked Suk Hee to do something.

106
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,450
Why are you getting so angry
all of a sudden?

107
00:05:40,650 --> 00:05:43,350
Did you have a bad dream last night?

108
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:44,350
He's right.

109
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:47,090
Grandfather and I have put up with this
for a long time.

110
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:51,260
Reheat Hong Ju's soup yourself.

111
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:54,130
It's fine, Mom. I'll just eat it.

112
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:56,890
And I told you to watch
how you address me.

113
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:58,630
Who are you calling "honey"?

114
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:01,170
Do it one more time,
and I won't let it slide.

115
00:06:01,430 --> 00:06:04,600
Honestly, honey.
It's not like I'm a stranger.

116
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,440
If I can't call my own husband "honey"...

117
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,140
There you go again.

118
00:06:10,170 --> 00:06:11,180
Mom.

119
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,680
Fine.

120
00:06:15,210 --> 00:06:16,450
All right, hon...

121
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:20,150
I mean, Chairman.

122
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:35,100
Your food's getting cold. Eat up, Jun Ho.

123
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:36,270
Oh, that's right.

124
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:39,200
Let me get you some hot soup.

125
00:06:40,810 --> 00:06:42,770
What's the special occasion?
You don't usually eat with me.

126
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,980
I'm not eating with you.
I'm eating with Mother.

127
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:48,580
Exactly. I'm glad you did.

128
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:49,980
Now, eat up.

129
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,850
There's plenty of soup,
so have more if you want.

130
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:53,480
Okay.

131
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,760
But, Mother.

132
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:00,990
Do you know
who Kang Baek Ho's parents were?

133
00:07:00,990 --> 00:07:02,660
Why do you want to know?

134
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:04,000
Why?

135
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,900
Did I strike a nerve?

136
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,170
Jun Ho.

137
00:07:07,970 --> 00:07:09,070
Well, you never know.

138
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:13,170
Maybe your birth parents
were as despicable as mine.

139
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,540
And I'm just curious...

140
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:16,840
why they'd make you
the majority shareholder...

141
00:07:16,910 --> 00:07:18,840
only to abandon you.

142
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:23,580
Does the fact I was adopted
suddenly make you feel superior?

143
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:26,520
Don't get the wrong idea, Kang Jun Ho.
I'm nothing like you.

144
00:07:26,850 --> 00:07:28,590
I don't have
the slightest inferiority complex...

145
00:07:28,590 --> 00:07:29,720
about being adopted.

146
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:32,920
- My birth parents are already dead.
- Are they?

147
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:34,660
How did they die?

148
00:07:35,030 --> 00:07:38,860
- What is it you're trying to find out?
- Why are you fighting in the morning?

149
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,530
It's true Baek Ho's parents passed away.

150
00:07:42,770 --> 00:07:46,370
His grandfather also died in a fire
when he was a child,

151
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,070
so he has no family left.

152
00:07:48,570 --> 00:07:49,870
A fire?

153
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,940
I should look into that.

154
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:54,610
Still, it's nice...

155
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:57,010
to have the whole family together
for a meal.

156
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,420
But it's not the whole family.

157
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:02,190
Father isn't here.

158
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:10,330
The person you called is unavailable...

159
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,770
Hwa Young isn't answering her phone.

160
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,000
I wonder if something happened.

161
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:21,470
If we're going to move in together,
we'll need to find a place to live.

162
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:27,550
Hey.

163
00:08:28,210 --> 00:08:29,650
Someone's in here.

164
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,020
Hey.

165
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:36,590
Yeom San Wol.

166
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,960
Jin Hong Ju.

167
00:08:40,490 --> 00:08:42,090
Can't you hear my voice?

168
00:08:43,130 --> 00:08:44,460
Answer me.

169
00:08:57,740 --> 00:08:58,740
Kang Hyuk.

170
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,610
Jun Ho.

171
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,080
No.

172
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,250
It can't end like this.

173
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:11,590
I endured so much under that old man.

174
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:15,730
I can't just wither away and die
in this hole.

175
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,100
No, that can't happen.

176
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,840
I'll get you a decent house,

177
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,610
so get ready to move right away.

178
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:32,110
No, Father.

179
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:34,310
Let's do it later. There's no rush.

180
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:39,520
I have so many regrets.

181
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:44,460
If I had given my blessing
when you said you were...

182
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:45,690
going to marry Dong Seok,

183
00:09:46,690 --> 00:09:48,460
you wouldn't have had to suffer so much.

184
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:53,430
The woman I love...

185
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:55,200
is you, Jung Suk Hee.

186
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:57,230
I'm marrying you,

187
00:09:57,940 --> 00:09:59,170
no matter what.

188
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:01,810
Pregnant?

189
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:04,480
From now on, this baby is mine.

190
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,280
I said she's my baby now!

191
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:07,810
No! Give me my baby back!

192
00:10:07,810 --> 00:10:09,110
Give her back!

193
00:10:09,250 --> 00:10:10,680
You can't do this!

194
00:10:13,180 --> 00:10:17,560
When I think about the past,
the present feels like a dream.

195
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,320
But...

196
00:10:19,590 --> 00:10:23,260
why did you used to tremble
whenever you saw Lee Kang Hyuk?

197
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,330
Back then,

198
00:10:25,660 --> 00:10:28,730
Chae Hwa Young said when it got dark...

199
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:30,370
Get rid of them after dark.

200
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,670
- to kill you and me.
- The mother and the daughter...

201
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:34,810
- She gave the order and left.
- Both of them.

202
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,870
So...

203
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:38,680
- to kill me,
- What are you doing? Go after her!

204
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:41,580
Lee Kang Hyuk,
who was chasing me with his thugs,

205
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,450
was scarier than the grim reaper.

206
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:46,950
I ran through the forest,
stumbling and falling.

207
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:49,150
- All the while,
- Over there!

208
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:52,020
I prayed that you in that warehouse...

209
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:54,690
wouldn't be found,

210
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:58,000
and I stalled for time however I could.

211
00:10:58,430 --> 00:11:02,770
Atop a cliff, during my final standoff
with Lee Kang Hyuk,

212
00:11:03,130 --> 00:11:06,140
I pretended to jump while holding you,

213
00:11:06,970 --> 00:11:08,270
and I threw myself off.

214
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:17,080
In my memory,

215
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:19,620
the last face of evil I saw...

216
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:22,790
- was Lee Kang Hyuk's.
- Stop.

217
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,520
That's enough.

218
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:26,690
Goodness.

219
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:29,130
Goodness, Eun Hye.

220
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:33,130
I won't let that bastard Lee Kang Hyuk,
get away with this.

221
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:37,100
I'm going to tear that bastard
limb from limb.

222
00:11:46,610 --> 00:11:49,750
Hwa Young went to the New York branch
without telling me?

223
00:11:50,780 --> 00:11:52,280
And she just left suddenly
in the middle of the night?

224
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:55,620
Even if it's meant to speed up
the inheritance process,

225
00:11:57,660 --> 00:11:59,860
this is all happening too suddenly.

226
00:12:00,930 --> 00:12:04,730
The person you have called is unavailable.
You will be connected to their voicemail.

227
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,570
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

228
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:12,470
- You called for me?
- Why can't I get a hold of CEO Chae?

229
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:16,610
She took an early flight
to the New York branch.

230
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:19,740
- Suddenly?
- Yes, it was a last-minute decision.

231
00:12:20,380 --> 00:12:23,050
The Chairman is handing
the company over to her,

232
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:24,680
so I believe this is
in preparation for that.

233
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:28,190
- He's handing over the company?
- But...

234
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:30,650
you didn't hear from her either?

235
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,620
- No.
- She's going on a long business trip,

236
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:37,230
and it's not like her to leave
without saying anything to you.

237
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:38,400
That's enough.

238
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:41,770
If you hear from her, please tell her
I have something urgent to report.

239
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:43,070
Understood.

240
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,870
Yes, Secretary Kim.

241
00:12:49,170 --> 00:12:50,980
CEO Chae's car is at the airport,

242
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:53,480
and you want me to take it in
for an inspection?

243
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:56,910
Yes, I'll take care of it.

244
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:05,160
(Director Ma Seo Rin)

245
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,430
Director Ma.

246
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:14,570
How did you arrive at these numbers?
Please let me know.

247
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:18,600
Did Chae Hwa Young confess?

248
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:25,010
It's not going well.
Isn't there an easier way to do this?

249
00:13:25,940 --> 00:13:28,210
In that case, how about this?

250
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:38,020
The prisoner's dilemma.

251
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:03,650
We've brought Lee Kang Hyuk.

252
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:06,580
Here.

253
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:11,920
Looks like Grandfather has already nabbed
Manager Lee Kang Hyuk.

254
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:13,320
Just like you said, Baek Ho,

255
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,290
the prisoner's dilemma strategy
will work, right?

256
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,860
Once Chae Hwa Young and Manager Lee...

257
00:14:17,190 --> 00:14:19,860
are overcome with the fear
that the other might betray them,

258
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:23,430
they'll have no choice
but to confess to save themselves.

259
00:14:24,770 --> 00:14:26,900
Let's hurry over and see how it's going.

260
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:31,180
Where are you two rushing off to?

261
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:35,210
It's a personal matter.
We have no obligation to report to you.

262
00:14:35,850 --> 00:14:37,880
A personal matter on company time?

263
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:41,120
Aren't you two getting a little
too comfortable around the office?

264
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,090
Separate your personal
and professional lives.

265
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:45,160
What can we do?

266
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,760
The Chairman called for us.

267
00:14:47,190 --> 00:14:51,100
It's a personal request
to set our wedding date.

268
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:55,200
- Lawyer Kang, I need a word.
- Didn't you hear her?

269
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:57,370
The Chairman called for us,
so we have to go now.

270
00:14:57,430 --> 00:14:58,900
Hear what I have to say first.

271
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:02,010
There's something I have to ask you.

272
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:04,010
It's very important.

273
00:15:07,010 --> 00:15:08,950
Jang Mi, you go on ahead. I'll catch up.

274
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:11,380
Okay. Be careful, Baek Ho.

275
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:17,520
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

276
00:15:20,220 --> 00:15:21,330
What is it you want to ask?

277
00:15:21,930 --> 00:15:24,530
I don't have time for a long talk.
Just get to the point.

278
00:15:24,530 --> 00:15:26,760
It's about the golden toad
in that box in your room.

279
00:15:27,670 --> 00:15:29,870
It's engraved
with Chairman Ma's family crest.

280
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,800
Do you have any idea why you have it?

281
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:35,140
This morning, you were asking
about my birth parents.

282
00:15:35,570 --> 00:15:36,740
And now you're curious about this?

283
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:40,710
I don't know why you're asking,
but the Chairman told me himself.

284
00:15:41,110 --> 00:15:43,110
My late biological grandfather
and the Chairman...

285
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:44,880
were the best of friends.

286
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,180
The golden toad and the golden spoon...

287
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:49,850
were gifts from the Chairman
for my first birthday.

288
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,160
What?

289
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:53,820
Your grandfather and the Chairman
were friends?

290
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:56,460
Why? Is that a problem?

291
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:59,500
So does the Chairman also know
that you're Choi Ha Joon?

292
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:01,730
Kang Jun Ho.

293
00:16:02,730 --> 00:16:04,400
How did you know my name was Choi Ha Joon?

294
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:08,640
I heard it from Mother.

295
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:11,910
It's not a lie. I heard it from CEO Chae.

296
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:14,950
Fine, so you know.

297
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:17,210
What do you want to ask me?

298
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,020
Stop beating around the bush
and just say it.

299
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,250
Isn't it strange?

300
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:25,360
The founder of Dream Group
personally engraved his family crest...

301
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,460
on your first-birthday gift.

302
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:27,620
If he was such a close friend,

303
00:16:28,230 --> 00:16:29,630
why didn't he take you in?

304
00:16:30,060 --> 00:16:33,660
- What?
- You lost your grandfather in a fire...

305
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,430
and were left an orphan,

306
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:38,270
but his so-called great friend
never took you in.

307
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:41,710
- He probably didn't know.
- But there were articles after the fire.

308
00:16:42,610 --> 00:16:45,880
All this time, the Chairman
never once looked for you,

309
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:48,580
the only living relative
of his best friend.

310
00:16:49,810 --> 00:16:50,950
Did he choose not to look for you?

311
00:16:52,050 --> 00:16:53,380
Or did he pretend he couldn't find you?

312
00:16:54,350 --> 00:16:55,750
Stop beating around the bush
and just say it.

313
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:58,720
What do you want from me?
Or do you already know? What is it?

314
00:16:58,790 --> 00:16:59,790
Say it!

315
00:17:00,660 --> 00:17:03,660
It's just frustrating
that you know nothing about the Chairman.

316
00:17:04,530 --> 00:17:06,000
Just because
he's Oh Jang Mi's grandfather,

317
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:08,230
does that automatically
make him a good person?

318
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:11,440
What on earth are you trying to say?

319
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:13,670
Kang Jun Ho.

320
00:17:14,870 --> 00:17:17,070
I'll handle my own business,
so stay out of it.

321
00:17:17,610 --> 00:17:19,580
Stop being so nosy. It doesn't suit you.

322
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:21,680
And let me give you some advice.

323
00:17:22,380 --> 00:17:25,120
Stop making Mom suffer,
and you should quit too.

324
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,750
Get away from Chae Hwa Young
and Lee Kang Hyuk...

325
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:29,650
and come back to Mom.

326
00:17:30,450 --> 00:17:31,760
It's your only way to survive.

327
00:17:36,190 --> 00:17:37,730
That arrogant punk.

328
00:17:40,900 --> 00:17:42,130
Give me some water.

329
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:44,870
Give me some water, please.

330
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:48,010
I said, give me some water.

331
00:17:56,850 --> 00:17:59,350
Secretary Kim, let go.
What do you think you're doing?

332
00:17:59,350 --> 00:18:01,020
- Sit down.
- Let go.

333
00:18:02,590 --> 00:18:03,590
Let go of me.

334
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:07,560
Secretary Kim, stop it.
What do you think you're doing?

335
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:09,030
How dare someone like you...

336
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,030
Untie me!

337
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:11,130
Untie me now.

338
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:14,700
Give me water. I'm dying of thirst.

339
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:18,570
Thirsty? You want some water?

340
00:18:25,710 --> 00:18:29,180
- How refreshing.
- Give me water. My throat is on fire.

341
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:30,810
Give me some water.

342
00:18:31,280 --> 00:18:33,280
Fine, I'll be generous.

343
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:43,830
Jung Suk Hee, please, spare me.

344
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:47,200
Secretary Kim, untie me.
Untie me right now!

345
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,240
Chae Hwa Young.

346
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:56,640
You seem to be under the delusion
that you're still the CEO of Dream Hotel.

347
00:18:57,010 --> 00:18:58,410
Snap out of it.

348
00:18:58,910 --> 00:19:00,410
I get it, so give me some water.

349
00:19:01,150 --> 00:19:03,780
I have to be alive to answer you, don't I?

350
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:07,680
Fine. To a beast who's dying of thirst,

351
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:10,690
I suppose I can spare a sip of water.

352
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:11,820
Open your mouth.

353
00:19:14,090 --> 00:19:17,860
I'll be kind and feed it to you.
Open wider.

354
00:19:25,870 --> 00:19:29,370
Jung Suk Hee, you witch.
So you're really determined to kill me.

355
00:19:29,770 --> 00:19:32,280
Just you wait.
I won't let you get away with this.

356
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,750
- Where's Mom?
- In the basement.

357
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:41,790
Don't worry.

358
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:44,560
Yeom San Wol is out too,
so no one's home right now.

359
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:45,820
Really?

360
00:19:49,390 --> 00:19:50,560
Confess now.

361
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:52,460
Confess that you did all of it.

362
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:55,500
Don't kid yourself, Jung Suk Hee.

363
00:19:56,570 --> 00:20:00,200
You can tie me up and threaten me,
but a forced confession...

364
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:04,070
or a recording made under duress...

365
00:20:04,410 --> 00:20:07,340
has no legal standing in court.

366
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:09,880
Code of Criminal Procedure, Article 309.

367
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,820
A confession obtained
through assault, intimidation...

368
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:15,690
or unlawful confinement
is inadmissible as evidence.

369
00:20:16,220 --> 00:20:17,920
Yes, you're right about that.

370
00:20:18,620 --> 00:20:21,120
But you only know half the story.

371
00:20:21,860 --> 00:20:24,630
You seem to think
you can get away with this,

372
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:29,170
but what you've done
is a death sentence in itself.

373
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:30,500
What?

374
00:20:32,240 --> 00:20:34,200
I'm the victim here.

375
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,440
Thirty years ago,

376
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:37,510
you locked me up in that villa...

377
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:40,840
and forcibly tore Seo Rin from my arms.

378
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:43,410
Article 287 of the Criminal Code.

379
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:46,280
Abduction and enticement of a minor.

380
00:20:46,850 --> 00:20:49,090
You stole the child I gave birth to...

381
00:20:49,420 --> 00:20:51,520
and passed her off
as the Dream Group heiress.

382
00:20:51,890 --> 00:20:54,890
You've lived in luxury all this time
because of that vicious scam.

383
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:56,730
On top of that,

384
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:58,660
you tried to kill my other daughter,
Jang Mi,

385
00:20:59,030 --> 00:21:01,060
and me.

386
00:21:01,430 --> 00:21:03,070
Get rid of them after dark.

387
00:21:03,570 --> 00:21:05,900
The mother and her daughter. Both of them.

388
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:07,700
It's already getting dark.

389
00:21:08,810 --> 00:21:12,140
My baby. I have to save you.

390
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,840
But how?

391
00:21:14,340 --> 00:21:16,280
To save Jang Mi,

392
00:21:16,580 --> 00:21:20,580
I had to hide my child
on the cold warehouse floor.

393
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:21,690
Live.

394
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:26,290
We have to survive
and see each other again.

395
00:21:36,230 --> 00:21:39,600
Then, to throw Lee Kang Hyuk
and his men off,

396
00:21:40,570 --> 00:21:42,510
I had no choice but to die.

397
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:56,620
Articles 250 and 254 of the Criminal Code.

398
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:58,290
Attempted murder.

399
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:01,660
Jung Suk Hee, that's...

400
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:05,100
No. I didn't do it.

401
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:07,060
You're making this up.
Stop making things up.

402
00:22:09,430 --> 00:22:11,370
Your crimes don't end there.

403
00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:13,400
You killed my father.

404
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:35,590
Dad, what's wrong? Tell me.

405
00:22:36,390 --> 00:22:37,390
Dad!

406
00:22:40,660 --> 00:22:43,600
You killed Seo Rin too.

407
00:22:44,100 --> 00:22:45,800
Say something, Chae Hwa Young.

408
00:22:47,870 --> 00:22:48,870
Seo Rin.

409
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:53,110
Thank you for being my daughter
all this time.

410
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:56,350
Now, you can rest in peace.

411
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,490
Why won't you look at me?

412
00:23:04,090 --> 00:23:06,860
When you look me in the eye,

413
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:08,990
does it remind you of Seo Rin,
whom you killed?

414
00:23:10,730 --> 00:23:11,730
Oh Jang Mi.

415
00:23:12,860 --> 00:23:13,860
Jang Mi.

416
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:15,630
Give me some water.

417
00:23:16,930 --> 00:23:18,540
I'm hungry.

418
00:23:18,540 --> 00:23:19,840
I'm starving.

419
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:24,370
They at least gave me water and food
in jail.

420
00:23:42,730 --> 00:23:44,190
Hey, you bastard.

421
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:47,900
Speak.

422
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:51,030
Tell me about...

423
00:23:51,770 --> 00:23:57,740
all the terrible things you two did
by deceiving me all this time.

424
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:03,350
Confess everything to me right now.

425
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:05,680
You bastard.

426
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:07,850
Lee Kang Hyuk, you bastard!

427
00:24:09,050 --> 00:24:10,150
Chairman.

428
00:24:11,050 --> 00:24:12,190
Don't tell me...

429
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:14,660
you know everything...

430
00:24:14,930 --> 00:24:16,160
You punk!

431
00:24:16,990 --> 00:24:18,730
You bastard.

432
00:24:18,860 --> 00:24:21,160
Did you really think...

433
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:25,440
I'd fall for your pathetic lies?

434
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:27,040
What about CEO Chae?

435
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:29,440
Where is she right now?

436
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:33,310
- Don't tell me she is also...
- That's right.

437
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:38,580
By now, she's in torment, just like you.

438
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:39,980
No.

439
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:44,350
- If you lay a finger on her...
- You bastard.

440
00:24:44,650 --> 00:24:49,060
And what will you do if I did?

441
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:52,730
The 30 years of suffering...

442
00:24:52,900 --> 00:24:56,600
my daughter, Eun Hye,
and my granddaughter, Jang Mi endured...

443
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:59,440
Nothing compares to that.

444
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:07,010
When I think of the terrible pain
my family endured,

445
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:11,010
my blood boils.

446
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:15,790
And my whole body trembles with rage,
you punk.

447
00:25:17,820 --> 00:25:22,860
Jang Mi lost her father
and her own sister,

448
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:24,590
Seo Rin.

449
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:30,200
My daughter, Eun Hye,
even lost her own child, you punk.

450
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:35,610
And after all that,
you two think you deserve to live?

451
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:39,640
You punk.

452
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:45,480
Lee Kang Hyuk, think this through.

453
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,920
Chae Hwa Young...

454
00:25:48,790 --> 00:25:51,660
has spent her life hiding behind you.

455
00:25:51,660 --> 00:25:55,390
She never got her own hands dirty.

456
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:58,360
She's never hit rock bottom,

457
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:02,370
and how long do you think
she can handle the pain?

458
00:26:02,900 --> 00:26:07,340
So you need to find a way
to save yourself.

459
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,540
Understood?

460
00:26:09,910 --> 00:26:12,980
If you come clean about everything now,

461
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:17,780
I might be merciful.

462
00:26:17,780 --> 00:26:18,820
All right?

463
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,250
Lee Kang Hyuk.

464
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:27,160
Tell me everything Chae Hwa Young did.

465
00:26:29,330 --> 00:26:30,590
Now!

466
00:26:31,160 --> 00:26:32,400
Tell me now!

467
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:45,340
Confess everything,
and I'll give you all this water.

468
00:26:45,810 --> 00:26:47,580
And your food, of course.

469
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:50,650
Chae Hwa Young, I'll do as you asked
and send you to jail.

470
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:53,080
It'll be much more comfortable
than this dark room.

471
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:55,250
At least you'll get
three meals a day there, right?

472
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:59,120
So spit it all out.

473
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,190
Just confess.

474
00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:03,730
Confess that you were behind
what happened to Seo Rin and Bok Gil,

475
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:05,100
and turn yourself in.

476
00:27:05,260 --> 00:27:08,830
Seriously.
Why are you all ganging up on me?

477
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:10,700
I told you, I don't know anything.

478
00:27:10,770 --> 00:27:13,870
Manager Lee Kang Hyuk
has probably started talking by now.

479
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,910
- What? Manager Lee?
- You know...

480
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:19,340
how relentless and terrifying
my grandfather can be...

481
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:21,410
once he makes up his mind, right?

482
00:27:21,710 --> 00:27:24,780
You think someone like Manager Lee
can hold out against him?

483
00:27:24,850 --> 00:27:25,980
Don't be ridiculous.

484
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:29,050
Even if Manager Lee
starts spouting nonsense,

485
00:27:29,350 --> 00:27:31,320
who's going to believe him
without any physical evidence?

486
00:27:31,390 --> 00:27:34,420
Chae Hwa Young, have you ever heard
of the "fruit of the poisonous tree"?

487
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:38,630
Yes, any confession or recording
we force out of you...

488
00:27:38,730 --> 00:27:40,600
might be considered the "poisonous fruit."

489
00:27:41,060 --> 00:27:43,000
But when Jang Mi uses it...

490
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:46,340
to find independent physical evidence,

491
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,470
it becomes a whole different story.

492
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:52,280
For example, the weapon
you used to murder Bok Gil,

493
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:54,240
the testimony and medical records...

494
00:27:54,310 --> 00:27:56,310
from the doctor
you bribed to help kill Seo Rin,

495
00:27:56,450 --> 00:27:57,850
or secondarily derived evidence...

496
00:27:57,850 --> 00:28:01,220
like the hidden bank accounts
of the people you hired.

497
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:03,650
All of that
would be perfectly admissible in court.

498
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:06,490
- But that...
- Grandfather probably has made...

499
00:28:06,490 --> 00:28:08,590
Manager Lee a very tempting offer
about now.

500
00:28:08,830 --> 00:28:11,430
That if he's the first one
to confess everything,

501
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:13,760
he can avoid jail time
and start over abroad.

502
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:15,730
And that my grandfather would give him
a huge amount of money...

503
00:28:15,730 --> 00:28:17,330
so he could live in luxury.

504
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:19,340
From Manager Lee's perspective,

505
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:22,670
wouldn't betraying you
be the much better deal?

506
00:28:22,910 --> 00:28:25,010
No, that's not true.

507
00:29:02,780 --> 00:29:04,350
(The First Man)

508
00:29:04,450 --> 00:29:06,480
Chae Hwa Young
just confessed to everything.

509
00:29:06,620 --> 00:29:09,550
She said you, Lee Kang Hyuk, were the one
who murdered Oh Bok Gil with a wrench.

510
00:29:09,650 --> 00:29:11,920
When was the last time
you saw CEO Chae at home?

511
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:15,290
I can't get a hold of Hwa Young.
Is something wrong?

512
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:17,790
I think CEO Chae has been kidnapped.

513
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:19,560
Lee Kang Hyuk betrayed you.

514
00:29:19,630 --> 00:29:21,200
You think I'm going to believe that?

515
00:29:21,330 --> 00:29:22,700
